snippet.title: Supermarket Mania Journey for Google Play, December 2019
snippet.description:
Serve customers and open new supermarkets in this time management adventure!
Running a grocery chain can be a lot of fun! Dive into this highly addictive time management game Supermarket Mania® Journey – and prepare to stay on your toes every single second. Join millions of players who are already fans of Nikki!

Play FREE on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.g5e.smmpg.android
